<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-13963] SecondaryIndexManagerTest.indexWithfailedInitializationIsNotQueryableAfterPartialRebuild is flaky</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13963</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The unit test &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/test/unit/org/apache/cassandra/index/SecondaryIndexManagerTest.java#L460-L476&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;SecondaryIndexManagerTest.indexWithfailedInitializationIsNotQueryableAfterPartialRebuild&lt;/a&gt; is flaky. Apart from &lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/All_Jobs/job/trunk_utest/2430/testReport/org.apache.cassandra.index/SecondaryIndexManagerTest/indexWithfailedInitializationIsNotQueryableAfterPartialRebuild/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;the CI results showing a 3% flakiness&lt;/a&gt;, the test failure can be locally reproduced just running the test multiple times. In my case, it fails 2-5 times for each 1000 executions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13110264">CASSANDRA-13963</key>
            <summary>SecondaryIndexManagerTest.indexWithfailedInitializationIsNotQueryableAfterPartialRebuild is flaky</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
